        <body>
            <div type="edition" xml:space="preserve"><head>Text</head><div n="1" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/>
                <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>ucius</ex></expan> Caesius <expan><abbr>L</abbr><ex>uci</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ilius</ex></expan> <lb n="2"/><expan><abbr>Cam</abbr><ex>ilia</ex></expan> Bassus <lb n="3"/>domo Pisauri <lb n="4"/><expan><abbr>vet</abbr><ex>eranus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>leg</abbr><ex>ionis</ex></expan> VII <expan><abbr>C</abbr><ex>laudiae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>iae</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>idelis</ex></expan> <lb n="5"/><expan><abbr>an</abbr><ex>norum</ex></expan> LIII <expan><abbr>stip</abbr><ex>endiorum</ex></expan> XXXII <lb n="6"/><expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>ic</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>s</abbr><ex>itus</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>e</abbr><ex>st</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>t</abbr><ex>estamento</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ieri</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>i</abbr><ex>ussit</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>h</abbr><ex>eres</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>osuit</ex></expan> </ab></div><div n="2" type="textpart"><ab><lb n="1"/> in <expan><abbr>f</abbr><ex>ronte</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>edes</ex></expan> VI in <expan><abbr>a</abbr><ex>gro</ex></expan> <expan><abbr>p</abbr><ex>edes</ex></expan> X
            </ab></div></div>
            <div type="commentary">
                <p>Nur handschriftlich, durch einen Kupferstich und ein Gemälde überliefert. Oberhalb der Inschrift männliche Büste in einer von Säulen flankierten Nische; darüber ein Waffenfries; kein Giebel erhalten; Z. 7 unterhalb des gerahmten Inschriftfeldes zwei Löwenköpfe. Höhenangabe nur ungefähr (nach der Überlieferung 6 Fuß). (B): CIL 03, 02014: Z. 5: XXXIII.</p>
            </div>
